snippet.textDisplay:
Mr. Li, 80, lives in Wuhan City, Hubei Province. He was diagnosed with the coronavirus in mid-January. After staying at a hospital for six days, doctors recommended that he move to a larger hospital.

The larger hospitals were overloaded with patients and turned him away. He had no choice but to stay at home. His condition worsened by the day. His kidneys failed, and he fell into a coma. He was finally admitted to Jinyintan Hospital in Wuhan in early February. Doctors there told his family that Mr. Li had little will to live, and they were unwilling to provide treatment.

One of Mr. Li's relatives practices Falun Dafa. After learning of Mr. Li's condition, the relative phoned him and suggested he recite the phrases, “Falun Dafa is good” and “Truthfulness-Compassion-Forbearance is good.”

Mr. Li could only remember part of the phrase, “Falun Dafa is good.” He sincerely recited the phrase every day, and his condition started to improve. His coronavirus symptoms gradually disappeared, and his spirit improved too.

On the seventh day, doctors carried out an RNA test, and the results were negative. He was released from the hospital the next day.

Mr. Li's friends and family were astonished by his miraculous recovery.
